=====================================================================
Installation on Ubuntu:
    sudo apt-get install mysql-server libmysqlclient-dev mysql-python

=====================================================================
Create user:
    CREATE USER 'name@localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';
    Note: if there're special characters in name or in host, quote like
          'name_1'@localhost;

Grant permission:
    GRANT ALL ON db1.* TO 'name@localhost';

Delete a user:
    DROP USER 'name@localhost';
===================================================================== 

